column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/494cbf8350d2c03cee4997067fa607a8fb49c4a3 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

I don't think that categorizing by programming language makes much sense here.
It's not forbidden to add C++ code to devtools if there is a reason to.
Let's categorize by functionality.
